						<div class="postbody">I immediately see a problem, you need to share the DMC channel's output level with the DAC value.  RAW PCM and DMC use the same counter.  Don't reset anything to zero.
<br />But that wouldn't account for unrecognizable sound.  Are you playing it back too fast?</div>

					
